# Rememorae Telegram Bot

A personal memory + reminder assistant that lives on Telegram.

## âœ¨ Features
- Log journal entries, prayers, study notes, and goals
- Search memories by keyword
- List your last 10 entries
- Set daily reminders (devotion time, focus time)
- Stores data locally in SQLite

## ğŸš€ Quick Deploy

### 1. Get Your Telegram Token
- Open Telegram, go to [@BotFather](https://t.me/botfather)
- Send `/newbot` â†’ follow prompts â†’ get your token.

### 2. Deploy to Railway
1. Create a free account at [Railway](https://railway.app) and connect your GitHub repo.
2. Add environment variables:
   - `TELEGRAM_TOKEN` â†’ your BotFather token
   - `TZ` â†’ e.g. `Africa/Lagos`
3. Deploy project â†’ check logs â†’ start using bot.

### 3. Commands
- `/log category | title | content` â†’ save a memory
- `/search keyword` â†’ find past entries
- `/list` â†’ list latest entries
- `/setreminder HH:MM | message` â†’ schedule daily reminder

